---
<BaseLayout {title}>
  <article class="container">
    <h1>troubleshooting</h1>
    <p>calm beats chaos. check power first, then signals, then logic.</p>

    <h2>flow</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>is +V on every chip? is 0 V common?</li>
      <li>no short between +V and 0 V (DMM continuity).</li>
      <li>inputs not floating (pull-ups/pull-downs present)?</li>
      <li>module pins at sane levels (3.3/5 V as expected)?</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="diagram" role="img" aria-label="DMM continuity check">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 560 150" width="100%" height="auto">
        <rect x="0" y="0" width="560" height="150" rx="16" fill="var(--card)"/>
        <text x="36" y="36" class="mono">beep mode</text>
        <rect x="110" y="20" width="150" height="80" rx="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"/>
        <text x="185" y="56" text-anchor="middle" class="mono">DMM</text>
        <text x="185" y="74" text-anchor="middle" class="mono mini">ðŸ””</text>
        <circle cx="140" cy="110" r="4" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="230" cy="110" r="4" fill="currentColor"/>
        <line x1="140" y1="110" x2="300" y2="110" stroke="currentColor"/>
        <line x1="230" y1="110" x2="420" y2="60" stroke="currentColor"/>
        <text x="430" y="64" class="mono">net A</text>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
